   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Year 12 of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, Pachon 21 for the arithmesis of Pachon. Paid by Sotas son of Didymos the son of Pathermouthios, his mother being Sote( ) for poll-tax of the twelfth year in the Treasury district twenty drachmas, that is, 20, with additional payments of ten bronze obols.</ab>
         </div>
